00:00:11.960 --> 00:00:15.320
mother. Why is that? You only get mitochondria from the

00:00:15.320 --> 00:00:18.870
mother. So, in this case the affected mother and unaffected

00:00:18.870 --> 00:00:22.794
father all of the children were affected. Both the males

00:00:22.794 --> 00:00:25.342
