00:00:31.320 --> 00:00:34.530
own three children, but does he pass mitochondria down to

00:00:34.530 --> 00:00:37.750
children? No, he doesn't. Only the mother does that, so they

00:00:37.750 --> 00:00:41.830
wouldn't be affected. Same thing over here. Male was affected

00:00:41.830 --> 00:00:44.810
